When his family's ship is attacked and his parents are taken captive, Adam (with the help of the swash-buckling Captain Voric) must find a way to save them from the diabolical and dastardly, Kalosian Space Pirates!
Spidey and Silk's time jaunt takes them all the way to their beginning...the science fair where they were bitten by the radioactive spider! Plus, Chronosaurus Rex revealed!
name: Chapter Four

volume.name: Amazing Spider-Man & Silk: Spider(Fly) Effect Infinite Comic

description: With the silver bullets flying, we've reach the final phase of our blood-soaked tale. Everything in this universe moves in cycles; with every new beginning must come an end, and with every end, a new beginning. Noah Packard has been following werewolves around the country for decades, will he find the peace he seeks? Will Teddy avenge the grizzly death of his father? Is tonight the night we hear the Lunar Cycles' final howl? Find out in the shocking conclusion of Scott Rosenberg's BAD MOON RISING.

A young woman recovers on a bench without any memory of either her name or what she is doing there. Leading the investigation with great difficulty, she tries to recover her not only her memory, but her whole identity.

What is she going to discover? A romantic past made of dramas and romances, or the commonplace existence of an ordinary woman? And if so, will she know how to become somebody, having been potentially anybody?

Something strange is brewing in the far off jungle. Meriem soon discovers she is being stalked while traveling through the jungle by the new apex predator of the Cretaceous Period. Can Meriem survive against this new threat, the dino riding Raptorella? A quirky new story from Devon Massey!

EFFIGY

After last issue's happy ending, it seems that all is right with the Charmed Ones. However, when a seemingly casual trip to see their father reveals something startling, everything that has happened to them is called into question. With the advent of the Old Ones approaching... will the Charmed Ones stand on the side of good or evil?
name: Effigy

description: A simple change of venues for one of Matt Murdock's cases becomes more complicated when The Punisher attempts to send the defendant away...permanently! If Daredevil and Blindspot want to get this mobster his day in court, it will take every ounce of wit and wile they have. All Frank needs to get what he wants is a bullet. The race is on!
name: Chapter One

description: Ten years after an aging Batman retired, Gotham City has sunk deeper into decadence and lawlessness in the opening chapter of Frank Miller's classic tale of the Dark Knight! Now, DC reprints an excerpt from the first issue of one of the best-selling graphic novels of all time at just $1.00, with pages from the DC ESSENTIALS CATALOGUE!

volume.name: DC Comics Essentials: Batman: The Dark Knight Returns

description:
A Final Blessing: The terrifying tale of horror's biggest icon comes to a close! As Dracula's minions paint London red, Van Helsing enters her final conflict with the vampire that can't die. Everything is on the line, and only one will survive!

description: Diana makes good use of her mother’s treasures as she finally confronts the Duke of Deception and his minions!
name: Chapter Seventeen

description: From the Shuster award winning creators of Least I Could Do and Gutters comes a loving nod to classic fantasy novels that manages to flip the genre on it's head. Unlikely heros cut a swath through a fantasy world that is extremely familiar and yet very different. A naive elven hunter makes an strange friend in an undead warlock and the two manage to make both enemies and friends as they fight the good fight against the Legaran Empire.

Adapted from the upcoming combat strategy game.

200 years after the fall of mankind, a malfunctioning war machine and a slave girl with the unique power to heal robotic minds must overcome their mutual distrust in order to rescue a friend from the robots intent on harvesting his life force.

Marie is a fighter who sells her skills to the highest bidder. With her friend and blood brother, William, she fights the 'Dragons' – strange creatures that hover on the borderline of reality.

Under the gaze of Edouard III, sovereign of England, a tournament has been organized, to fight monsters made of pasteboard, and beautiful Marie will be the guest of honor... But the young woman is still looking for her brother Amaury, sold as slave when he was eight years old. And to overcome the French armies, the king of England schemes to call upon dark forces - the real monsters, made of horror and hatred, which Marie has been fighting for a long time...

Knights are competing against each other to impress noble ladies, swords are colliding, worlds are tearing apart, and atrocities are showing up... And Marie has to choose her side.
name: Amaury 2/2

description: A pack of goblins work to track down the creatures, leading to a violent confrontation, with tragic consequences.

While the United States are accused of wanting to found a New World Order, the disasters continue around the world, causing riots, tensions to rise, and the possibility of war.

What really happened to the Titanic, which led it to navigate at full steam? And a probe has been sent into the blue hole of the Bahamas, but what is hiding on the other side of the mirror?
name: Mantique 2/2

description: Luke Keith and Jeremy Fiest bring SEVEN PERCENT to its thrilling conclusion as 034 gains access to his full capabilities and faces down his past.

Tricked by Hel, Thor leads an army against Hel’s father Loki, even as Ares battles Ra, believing Ra is protecting the god who assassinated Zeus. Events reach a tipping point as more gods choose sides, plunging the Pantheons into the all-out war seen in SMITE.
name: Part 3

description:
"If it is by the hand of God that I cast out demons, then the Kingdom of God has come upon you." Luc, XI:20. 2000 years of secrets.

One Gospel written by Judas. A relic coveted since the Crusades. Inquisitors willing to do anything to seize it. A world which could go over to fanaticism... What worse could happen?

The worst? The worst would be that Angelo, the Sicilian killer, is back and that he is not happy!

And indeed, Angelo is back, and seemingly raised from the dead! Like Lazarus, but a whole lot more militant. Merciless, crueler than before... Angelo is about to dispense his own form of benediction.
name: Godfinger 2/2

description: The head of the CIA's ghost unit has been murdered but the team finally has a lead on their opponent, sending them to Paris and into the mysterious Russian's personal history. Can Calley keep a grip on reality long enough to stop the next step in the Russian's master plan? JOSHUA STARNES and LISANDRO ESTHERREN spin the spy thriller in never before seen ways as SPOOK races towards its epic conclusion!

These Same Stars

The thrilling conclusion to TransCat's epic search for her lost lady love! What waits behind this door? Loving reunion? Or tragedy? The answers to all this and more lie within these hallowed pages!
name: These Same Stars

description:
2166, THE ERA OF THE APOCALYPSE ENTERS ITS FINAL PHASE - THE LAST TIMES.

In a world dominated by religious zeal and politics, in the New Jerusalem that has become the center of the world, a devastating God has been created by a group of religious fanatics.

Yiu, a mercenary killer paid by the clergy, is the only one who can beat the newborn demon!
name: In Hell
